&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About this role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Boulder Care is looking for a Director of Payer Partnerships to lead our charge into the next generation of value-based behavioral health care. If you&#39;re a sales leader who thrives on closing complex deals, loves the strategy behind value-based care, and wants your work to directly expand access to addiction and behavioral health treatment, this is your seat at the table.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll own the full sales cycle for new payer partnerships and lead the transition of existing fee-for-service relationships into innovative, outcomes-based contracts. Your wins translate directly into expanded access to care — and into Boulder&#39;s growth across new markets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Payer Sales &amp;amp; Negotiate Contracts (60%)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the end-to-end sales cycle for new payer partnerships — from first pitch to signed Value-Based Care (VBC) and pay-for-performance contracts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead strategic renegotiations with existing fee-for-service partners, transitioning them into progressive risk-sharing and VBC frameworks built around Boulder&#39;s outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be the primary negotiator on contract terms, rates, and performance metrics — crafting agreements that are financially sound and mutually beneficial.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build compelling, data-driven value propositions tailored to each health plan&#39;s population and strategic priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the full contracting lifecycle, from discovery through redlining, execution, and a smooth handover to our Partner Success team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shape Strategy &amp;amp; Build Your Pipeline (25%)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage a robust pipeline of payer prospects, using CRM tools to forecast revenue and report on key sales metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct market research on regional payer landscapes, competitor positioning, and regulatory shifts shaping VBC opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and prioritize high-value targets, including Medicaid Managed Care Organizations (MCOs), Medicare Advantage plans, and commercial health plans.&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate &amp;amp; Share Market Insight (15%)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share market feedback with internal teams to help shape product development, pricing, and clinical program design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Operations and Partner Success after signing to ensure smo

&lt;p&gt;Don&#39;t see any openings that suit your interests and skills? Don&#39;t be deterred! We&#39;d still love to hear from you. We&#39;re always excited to hear about talented A-players interested in joining our Boulder team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To be considered for new positions as they open up, simply fill out the General Interest Application and we&#39;ll get in touch with you if there&#39;s a fit. We also encourage you to check back frequently and apply for future openings.&lt;/p&gt;
